Description: Elasticsearch JVM heap monitor with Slack alerts
 A lightweight daemon that monitors Elasticsearch cluster health and
 per-node JVM heap usage, sending alerts to a Slack incoming webhook
 when configurable thresholds are exceeded.
 .
 Features include automatic cluster discovery, endpoint failover,
 recovery notifications, and an alert cooldown to prevent alert floods.
